title: Quantumnauts 1 Speed Of Light Space Pirates And Multiverses
description:
run winsetup.exe to change some game settings if you need to
run QUANTUMNAUTS.exe to play the game

the game itself is just like an old adventure games from the 90s, and not the best one at that to. So what really bugs me is why it is so damn hard to find this piece of crap? I mean I could understand that torrents have no seeds, but going all out to clean it from all the file sharing servers so I have to go through like ten pages of google search results before finally getting it from some megashares or something whats up with that??? did some one really believes that he could actually get some serious money from that game??? dude thats fucking pathetic.
